      <title>韩国锌业股价因股权出售计划调查报告而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/korea-zinc-shares-sink-after-report-of-share-sale-plan-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前当地媒体报道称，韩国市场监管机构可能要求韩国锌业公司修改其 18 亿美元的股票出售计划，此后该公司股价一度暴跌 23%，延续前一天的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/korea-zinc-shares-sink-after-report-of-share-sale-plan-probe</guid>
